OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy and
OL,6,Fmurky evening with some mist and
OL,7,Fpatchy drizzle. Remaining rather
OL,8,Fcloudy through the rest of the night,
OL,9,Fbut some clearer spells developing
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA mainly dry day with a
OL,13,Fgood deal of cloud, but some brighter
OL,14,For sunnier spells possible at times,
OL,15,Fespecially for Orkney.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FFairly cloudy with heavy and thundery
OL,19,Foutbreaks of rain on Thursday and
OL,20,FFriday alongside risk of haar. Fresher
OL,21,Fon Saturday with a few showers.
